TITLE: Checking Permissions with CASL in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the defined ability instance to check various permissions on different subjects.
SOURCE: https://github.com/stalniy/casl/blob/master/docs-src/src/content/pages/guide/intro/en.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
